// @test regression/unused-vars-method-body
// @description A variable used only inside a `method` body must not be reported as unused. The SemanticAnalyzer never walked MethodDeclaration bodies or collected their params. See plan/31 Finding 3.
// @expects parse: success
// @expects warnings: 0
//@version=6
indicator("x")
float offsetVal = 5.0
method shifted(float value) =>
    value + offsetVal
plot(close.shifted())
